  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F and grease a 9x5-inch loaf pan.",
    "Blend dates, almond milk, coconut oil, maple syrup, vanilla, and cinnamon until smooth.",
    "Whisk oat flour, chickpea flour, baking powder, baking soda, salt, and cinnamon in a bowl.",
    "Pour the wet mixture into the dry ingredients and whisk until just combined.",
    "Fold in shredded coconut.",
    "Pour batter into the prepared loaf pan and smooth the top.",
    "Bake for 45 minutes, or until a toothpick comes out clean.",
    "Let the cake cool in the pan for 10 minutes, then transfer to a wire rack to cool completely.",
    "Slice and serve with a drizzle of maple syrup or plant‑based yogurt if desired."
